{"tid":1891231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"工聯會做口罩＝用庫房錢為9月做選舉工程","createTime":"2020-02-21T16:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T16:14:21.000Z","uid":82302,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c2e050d86a1be438b1512d45fde845833182d0","tid":1891231,"uid":82302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200221/large/1582216436_98c8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200221%2Flarge%2F1582216436_98c8.gif&h=dbc20415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工聯會仿製CSi口罩派街坊<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情持續，本港口罩供不應求。工聯會昨日宣佈早前設立的口罩工場成功生產首批口罩，首批10萬個仿「CSi」式樣口罩，將透過<span style=\"color: red;\">「地區社團」及「行業工會」優先派給長者及基層市民</span>，不作公開發售。工聯會預計3月下旬全自動生產機器抵達生產線後，日產量可提升至10萬個，但未有回應有關口罩日後會否作商業發售。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會昨日舉行記者會，工聯會理事長黃國、榮譽會長陳婉嫻及副理事長陳鄧源均戴上該批口罩。陳鄧源指工場以懲教署工場（懲教工業，CSi）作藍本，原材料與工場所用一樣。現時工場有約200萬個口罩的原材料，預計口罩工場營運至少半年，未來會考慮在口罩上加上「工聯會」壓花字樣。記者所見，<span style=\"color: red;\">口罩的布料顏色與「CSi」口罩一樣</span>。<br />\n<br />\n拒回應會否商業發售<br />\n黃國指，<span style=\"color: red;\">現時工場共有11部半自動機器配合義工操作及包裝，首階段可月產10萬個</span>。他表明首批口罩不作公開發售，只作慈善用途，免費派發長者、前線清潔、保安、運輸工人及基層市民，料每日有1,000人受惠。由於口罩須接受品質檢測，預計要多一至兩星期才能派發。他稱，下月底全自動生產機器到達後，便會開展第二階段生產，屆時可日產10萬個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n陳婉嫻未有回應工聯會口罩日後會否作商業發售，僅表明支持政府將口罩列作戰略物資作抗疫之用。保險界立法會<span style=\"color: red;\">陳健波</span>昨日以立橋保險集團CEO身份，出席現場進行100萬元支票捐贈儀式；另外<span style=\"color: red;\">廣東社團總會、工銀亞洲及青海嘉潤</span>亦向工聯會捐款合共260萬元。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source： <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200221/3QRV3B5NDMHYQAOK64WB2IRYRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2F3QRV3B5NDMHYQAOK64WB2IRYRU%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AABjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e64202c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2F3QRV3B5NDMHYQAOK64WB2IRYRU%2F&h=8bb2fb41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200221/3QRV3B5NDMHYQAOK64WB2IRYRU/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n公民黨郭家麒也質疑政府的預算不合理，指<span style=\"color: red;\">政府以3元一個購入口罩</span>，容許商人「趁火打劫」，又指<span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會亦有生產口罩，有私相授受之嫌</span>。張建宗先解釋，抗疫基金並非給予局長和司長個別使用，亦非在個別的人士，而在提升抗疫裝備。商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華就表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">每條口罩生產線最多只獲300萬元資助，之後的生產線則最多資助200萬元</span>，強調價錢只是上限。工聯會陸頌雄亦發言反擊，稱工聯會的口罩只派不賣，又強指民主派政黨因工聯會派口罩而「酸溜溜」才提出質疑。<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200221/JCFFIRVBBMOFCPCCXS4RHDF4WU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2FJCFFIRVBBMOFCPCCXS4RHDF4WU%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AABjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c71d6585\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2FJCFFIRVBBMOFCPCCXS4RHDF4WU%2F&h=6f1e32d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200221/JCFFIRVBBMOFCPCCXS4RHDF4WU/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n財委會審議撥款期間，多名議員質疑，政府計劃以平均每個口罩 3 元的價錢包銷是過高，公民黨議員陳淑莊指，<span style=\"color: red;\">根據 2013 年的報道，懲教署生產的口罩只售一毛三仙</span>；民主黨尹兆堅追問政府會否限制廠商售買口罩的最高毛利率，或考慮由政府生產口罩。公民黨楊岳橋則問及，政府會如何分配包銷得來的口罩，及政府會否參考澳門及台灣做法，將包銷的口罩直接賣給市民。<br />\n在會上麥美娟提到，<span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會自設口罩工廠生產時，根本不知有此基金</span>，他們成立工廠是不想坐等政府援手，「我哋係只送不賣嘅！」，麥美娟稱未知會否申請基金。她指有投資者想注資生產口罩，向生產力促進局詢問卻未有提供協助，結果他把生產線轉到澳門，希望政府向有心人提供技術支援，以及設立「口罩生產熱線」援助。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source： <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-59-%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-300-%E5%84%84%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%8A%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-59-%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-300-%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259D%25BE%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AABjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=496f2873\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-59-%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-300-%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259D%25BE%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%2F&h=1d49e0be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-59-%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-300-%E5%84%84%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%8A%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 11部半自動機器、全自動機器、廠房、原材料、人手、品質檢測差唔多咩都ready曬咁濟，仲快過wiki, kk kwong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 眾所周知，依家最難係搵原材料，但工聯會既口罩顏色同「CSi」一樣，究竟佢地原材料從何而黎？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 懲教署生產的口罩只售$0.13，點解港共以每個$ 3 買？一條生產線300萬元、其後每條額外200萬元資助，你地諗下工聯會每個月可以攞幾多？ 今次仲唔fat fat?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[size=4]<br />\n[size=4]4. 口罩會派俾邊個，你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再掛住飲香檳，人地做緊野啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1a6e736591e2958b830691698097285af7a8b4c1","tid":1891231,"uid":271894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"其實部機係咪係監獄搬出嚟"},{"pid":"3a4658b1943337d09e9d970850f121cd8db4a7eb","tid":1891231,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4c2cc401e003249f3e63e6bbdc79b0d82dc2cc","tid":1891231,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"11部機，大陸政府有都留俾自己，點解會買到咁多"},{"pid":"5692f1bd798b07ff2903453260fcf914f389c5c6","tid":1891231,"uid":216441,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFvHX0Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFvHX0Z.gif&h=842a2f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實我地呢邊都好畀心機㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb86eea338b5c884218552a399c3d0794d1cca00","tid":1891231,"uid":143151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"想講下 屋企樓下 個前少數派區議員死唔斷氣<br />\n派大公報 加代訂食物同清潔用品<br />\n但現屆個個乜都未開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚擔心"},{"pid":"13555244a928ecfdf908680cc9f67533da602629","tid":1891231,"uid":235824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"即係政府收埋好多機唔用<br />\nE家機就分俾民賤.  材料又分俾民賤<br />\n民賤0成本.  只需出人手.   就可以賺返政府每個3蚊<br />\n<br />\n林鄭正仆街    屌   永遠唔撚識進步  屌"},{"pid":"af0f3ee5f6c307711ae6821a7b14c6c6707b24df","tid":1891231,"u